	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hah! You think thats bad? Wait until you get into the 40s. You'll still be using the same heal spell that you got at lvl 29. <br><br>People will invite you to group thinking you can keep them healed up like a cleric can and then they get pissed when you just can't do it. Sure we have heal spells but at this point the palidans and rangers are about as good a healer as shamans and druids (druids are stuck with same healing spells until 50s too).<br><br>They just can't seem to comprehend that shamans purpose changes at a certain point. At these levels we're primarily buffers/debuffers with healing as a backup. My main spells when I'm in a group right now (I'm 48th level) is my Malo and Togor series of spells with healing only as backup.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
